WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:01.400
What are you still doing?

2
00:00:01.400 --> 00:00:03.600
Hurry up and give it to Zhao Ruolan and Ma Shoufu

3
00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:05.266
And the whole village apologized

4
00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:06.766
Leader

5
00:00:06.766 --> 00:00:10.266
It was the two of them who bullied us

6
00:00:10.333 --> 00:00:13.266
Why do we have to apologize to him in turn?

7
00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:15.700
Zhao Ruolan is allowed to cheat

8
00:00:15.700 --> 00:00:17.633
He should be punished

9
00:00:17.700 --> 00:00:19.566
What about us today?

10
00:00:19.566 --> 00:00:22.066
I already understood it very clearly on the way here

11
00:00:22.066 --> 00:00:23.400
It's your family

12
00:00:23.700 --> 00:00:25.900
Bullying Zhao Ruolan from start to finish

13
00:00:25.900 --> 00:00:27.366
Now I'm going to give you two options.

14
00:00:27.366 --> 00:00:29.066
Ask me to apologize honestly

15
00:00:29.066 --> 00:00:31.900
Want me to put you on the unwelcome list

16
00:00:31.900 --> 00:00:34.300
Let you never come to the building again

17
00:00:35.266 --> 00:00:36.066
Don't lead

18
00:00:36.066 --> 00:00:38.466
I have been in the building for decades

19
00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:40.566
Half of the assets are in the building

20
00:00:40.566 --> 00:00:42.366
I can't leave the building

21
00:00:42.366 --> 00:00:43.600
Yes, leader.

22
00:00:43.666 --> 00:00:45.600
You give me another chance.

23
00:00:45.900 --> 00:00:47.700
Aren't you arrogant?

24
00:00:47.700 --> 00:00:49.666
Aren't you waiting to be slapped in the face?

25
00:00:49.666 --> 00:00:52.033
Satisfy you now

26
00:00:52.200 --> 00:00:53.166
Are you not happy?

27
00:00:53.166 --> 00:00:54.933
I'm going to give you one last chance.

28
00:00:54.933 --> 00:00:57.200
That is to honor the bet with Zhao Ruolan

29
00:00:57.400 --> 00:00:58.566
Otherwise

30
00:00:58.566 --> 00:00:59.900
Don't blame me for being rude

31
00:01:00.066 --> 00:01:01.366
Just lie to you

32
00:01:01.533 --> 00:01:03.166
Can't help us

